Escape Room Game Insturctions

Phase 1
1. Solve the equation on the box
2. Stand in front of Lidar a distance away based on solved equations
3. Display on LCD move to move to Phase 2

Phase 2
4. Pitch the PTU to values given in the equation to unlock pin 1
5. Roll the PTU to values given in the equation to unlock pin 2
6. Yaw the PTU to value given on LCD screen to unlock pin 3

Phase 3
7. Play Pop the balloon game => given hint on how to play next game
8. Play repeat after me game => given hint on how to unlock door with PTU
9. Move PTU 1st pitch to unlock pin 1 then roll to unlock pin 2 to unlock the door!
